commits.message: added initial interactive page to browse the budget;
Made changes with the create user
added description to the budgets table;
switched from `insert` to `replace` so that it can be lazily run/rerun without necessarily first dropping the database;
added class to model a budget that is not time-bound; rearranged the parameters to the constructor for class User; Added methods to fetch budget/entries data from database;
moved logout button and added a "logged in as" short text;
made main direct jsp index file redirect to the main servlet index
Completed login/logout logic -- redirects to home page if valid credentials, else redirect to the login page again; Removed .html suffix to links;
additional demo test case to show how to run sql queries;
added ability to connect to the database;
added sql file which will later be used to pre-populate the database with test data;
refactored output of sample user data;
